{"data":[{"name":"92:1","price":"سوگند به شب، هنگامی ‌که [همه چیز را] بپوشانَد،","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6059,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshā ","translations":["By the night","when","it covers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1640],[3,1640,2775]]}},{"name":"92:2","price":"و سوگند به روز، هنگامی‌ که آشکار شود،","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا تَجَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6060,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā tajallā ","translations":["And the day","when","it shines in brightness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","tajallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2570],[3,2570,3855]]}},{"name":"92:3","price":"و سوگند به ذاتی که نر و ماده را آفرید،","arabic":"وَمَا خَلَقَ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6061,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā khalaqa al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And He Who","created","the male","and the female","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","khalaqa","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1260],[3,1260,2170],[4,2170,4415]]}},{"name":"92:4","price":"که یقیناً سعی [و تلاش] شما مختلف [و نیک و بد] است.","arabic":"إِنَّ سَعۡيَكُمۡ لَشَتَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6062,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"inna saʿyakum lashattā ","translations":["Indeed","your efforts","(are) surely diverse","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","saʿyakum","lashattā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,2330],[3,2330,3655]]}},{"name":"92:5","price":"و اما کسی‌ که [در راه الله] ببخشد و پرهیزگاری نماید","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أَعۡطَىٰ وَٱتَّقَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6063,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man aʿṭā wa-ittaqā ","translations":["Then as for","(him) who","gives","and fears","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","aʿṭā","wa-ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2150],[3,2150,3050],[4,3050,4725]]}},{"name":"92:6","price":"و [وعدۀ الله و سخنان] نیک را تصدیق کند،","arabic":"وَصَدَّقَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6064,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣaddaqa bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And believes","in the best","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣaddaqa","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2425]]}},{"name":"92:7","price":"به زودی انجام [کار خیر و] آسانی [= اعمال نیکو و انفاق در راه الله] را برایش آسان می‌کنیم.","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡيُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6065,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'yus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] ease","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'yus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1790],[2,1790,3725]]}},{"name":"92:8","price":"و اما کسی‌که بخل ورزد و بی‌نیازی بجوید،","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۢ بَخِلَ وَٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6066,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man bakhila wa-is'taghnā ","translations":["But as for","(him) who","withholds","and considers himself free from need","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","bakhila","wa-is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2630],[3,2630,3250],[4,3250,4555]]}},{"name":"92:9","price":"و [وعدۀ الله و سخنانِ] نیک را تکذیب کند،","arabic":"وَكَذَّبَ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6067,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wakadhaba bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And denies","the best","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wakadhaba","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2455]]}},{"name":"92:10","price":"به زودی انجام دشواری [= اعمال شر و پلید] را برایش آسان می‌سازیم [و انجام کار خیر را بر او سخت می‌گردانیم]؛","arabic":"فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُۥ لِلۡعُسۡرَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6068,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"fasanuyassiruhu lil'ʿus'rā ","translations":["Then We will ease him","towards [the] difficulty","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fasanuyassiruhu","lil'ʿus'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,3555]]}},{"name":"92:11","price":"و در هنگام [مرگ و] ورود به دوزخ، دارایی او سودی به حالش نخواهد داشت.","arabic":"وَمَا يُغۡنِي عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥٓ إِذَا تَرَدَّىٰٓ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6069,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yugh'nī ʿanhu māluhu idhā taraddā ","translations":["And not","will avail","him","his wealth","when","he falls","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yugh'nī","ʿanhu","māluhu","idhā","taraddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1540],[3,1540,2130],[4,2130,4670],[5,4670,5280],[6,5280,6595]]}},{"name":"92:12","price":"مسلماً هدایت [بندگان] بر [عهدۀ] ماست.","arabic":"إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا لَلۡهُدَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6070,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿalaynā lalhudā ","translations":["Indeed","upon Us","(is) the guidance","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿalaynā","lalhudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,2250],[3,2250,3435]]}},{"name":"92:13","price":"و محققاً آخرت و دنیا [نیز] از آنِ ماست.","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لَنَا لَلۡأٓخِرَةَ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6071,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-inna lanā lalākhirata wal-ūlā ","translations":["And indeed","for Us","(is) the Hereafter","and the first (life)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-inna","lanā","lalākhirata","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1360],[2,1360,2110],[3,2110,3550],[4,3550,5025]]}},{"name":"92:14","price":"من شما را از آتشی شعله‌ور بیم دادم","arabic":"فَأَنذَرۡتُكُمۡ نَارٗا تَلَظَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6072,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-andhartukum nāran talaẓẓā ","translations":["So I warn you","(of) a Fire","blazing","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-andhartukum","nāran","talaẓẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2650],[2,2650,4010],[3,4010,5555]]}},{"name":"92:15","price":"که جز بدبخت‌ترین [مردم] در آن نیفتد؛","arabic":"لَا يَصۡلَىٰهَآ إِلَّا ٱلۡأَشۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6073,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yaṣlāhā illā al-ashqā ","translations":["Not","will burn (in) it","except","the most wretched","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yaṣlāhā","illā","al-ashqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,3279],[3,3279,3899],[4,3899,5524]]}},{"name":"92:16","price":"[همان] کسی ‌که [آیات ما را] تکذیب کرد و روی گرداند","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6074,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["The one who","denied","and turned away","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2000],[3,2000,3405]]}},{"name":"92:17","price":"و به زودی پرهیزگارترین [مردم] از آن دور نگه داشته می‌شود.","arabic":"وَسَيُجَنَّبُهَا ٱلۡأَتۡقَى","category":["92 (Al-Lail)","Al-Lail","Surah Al-Lail"],"ayahNumber":6075,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa","meta":{"transliteration":"wasayujannabuhā al-atqā ",